Me](https://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/in-
afghanistan-375x281.jpg)](http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=371399072931289&set=a.127627373975128.24855.121186644619201&type=1&permPage=1)

